<h1>VLDB 2025: Registration</h1>
<p>Each research or industrial paper must have an in-person author registration, even if the paper is presented by a student. The author registration refers to a regular "Conference-Only" or "Workshop+Conference" registration. If an author has more than one paper, they will only need to pay for one author registration, which may cover multiple papers.</p>

<p>Each workshop paper must also have an author registration, even if the paper is presented by a student. The author registration refers to a regular "One-Day Workshop" or "Workshop+Conference" registration. If an author has more than one workshop paper, they will only need to pay for one author registration, which may cover multiple workshop papers.
The conference will have two components: an in-person component and a virtual component.
The in-person component will take place from August 28 to September 1.
The virtual component will take place on September 1.</p>

<p>In-person registration allows attendees to also participate in the virtual component without paying an additional virtual registration fee.</p>

<p><br/></p>
